{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 Ze Musette Organ\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 An {\b easy to use} jsfx instrument reminiscent of some italian electronic organs of the late 70s.\par}
